{
  "stem": "12491.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would send out the signal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- I didn't know how many at that time-- the ones who are assigned to this underground would come to the kitchen, grab the weapons, and try to defend ourselves to last for six hours until [INAUDIBLE] the underground, hoping that they will come to our help.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It didn't come to that because the Germans just capitulated on the 8th of May, and we did not need to use these weapons, at least not for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We did use them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But this is a story in its own way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I wish to retract-- [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] Now I'm getting a little bit confused myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You have to retract, to a point, the Germans-- the Germans evacuated many places in the East.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Schindler travelled there, and somehow he got contacts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was allowed to take all of the goods out of these places where they evacuated which the Germans themselves-- the armies-- could not take.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He brought it all into the camp, and he was distributing tobacco and cookies and cakes and everything else to the people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "All he organized in that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He also convinced the Germans to bring to his factory many truckloads of fabrics from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And these were fabrics-- shirt materials, slacks materials, coat materials, heavy, light.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My God, this was a factory filled to about 10 or 15 feet high.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You had to climb and walk all over that in order to see it all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And eventually, this material was distributed among all the people at Schindler's, and everybody took his package with him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I, being one of those, eventually who found out 28 or 30 underground people were given special privileges.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We took much more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Which I eventually sold in Krakow after we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
